lead_paragraph: Formula One stewards rejected Ferrari's request for a review of Sebastian Vettel's Mexican Grand Prix penalty on Friday, arguing that the Italian team had not presented any new evidence to warrant such a move.

headline.print_headline: F1 Stewards Rule Out Review of Vettel's Penalty
